    <measure>Needle passes</measure>
    <time_frame>Estimated 10 minutes</time_frame>
    <description>Attempt to place needle into the interlaminar foramina. Needle tip movements toward midline and cephalad were counted as s single pass. Additional passes were counted when the needle was returned to a plane parallel to the skin.</description>
  </secondary_outcome>
